headline: CommonWealth Central Credit Union Invests in the Future with Jack Henry
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) announced today that CommonWealth Central Credit Union (CommonWealth) selected Jack Henry to modernize its technology infrastructure and support future growth.
